<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我其實<delay20 />想用更大一點的捕蟲網，<delay8 />
<delay8 />去抓更大隻一點的昆蟲──！<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過如果捕蟲網太大的話，<delay8 />
可能連我自己<delay20 />都拿不動啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要我的釣竿在手，<delay20 />
不管那條魚有多大隻，<delay8 />
我都有自信把牠成功釣上來──！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />首先要做的事情，<delay8 />
就是釣起大隻的稻田魚！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來吧，<delay8 />我要開始認真了──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />澆花壺真是好用啊！<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且還可以馬上<delay8 />
用它來沖澡耶──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有了這個東西，以後不管流再多汗，
都可以隨時拿它來沖澡了──！</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我這把雨傘，<delay frames="40" />
是為了訓練<delay8 />特別訂製的喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它的重量是一般雨傘的10倍！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要撐著它就不會淋濕身體，<delay20 />
但我的手臂<delay8 />會發出慘叫啊──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
